_:N9b5ae82de36e4189a5a0bf529413da86 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Adrian Hannell was appointed Interim Director of Finance and Digital at the Legal Aid Agency in September 2017.</p>\n\n<p>He joined the Legal Aid Agency in April 2016 as Deputy Director of Finance. Before that, Adrian worked as finance director for a number of businesses within Capita PLC, and also held a variety of finance roles at Alliance Boots.\nAdrian began his career at Ernst &amp; Young where he qualified as a chartered accountant.</p>\n" .
